{"tid":1570462,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"銅鑼灣站部分出口有多批防暴警　崇光下午2時關店","createTime":"2019-09-15T05:46:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T06:53:37.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c39dfd950ea0dec08c76bcfbe2cc1c68ce8772bc","tid":1570462,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:46:43.000Z","msg":"民陣發起銅鑼灣集會遊行，上訴被駁回後宣布取消活動，有網民發起下午到港島行街。<br />\n<br />\n中午時分，港鐵銅鑼灣站部分出口，有多批防暴警員，他們配備伸縮警棍、手槍等防暴裝備，當中有人手持防暴圓盾，有警員身穿寫有警察字樣的黑色背心，胸前掛上委任證，亦有警員帶著黑色頭盔及索帶。<br />\n<br />\n崇光百貨宣布將在下午2時關店，店內廣播表示，基於顧客及職員安全為首要考慮，將於2時正關店。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480645-20190915.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480645-20190915.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mBSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=b1bd965f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480645-20190915.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fc475fc4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480645-20190915.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"60d2212459258d27825ed1278aea99a2d3403cb1","tid":1570462,"uid":275975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:47:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">太古無退路！小心係太古俾狗圍捕！</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KBt0dwQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKBt0dwQ.jpg&h=5c8a54fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4jZOnqe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4jZOnqe.jpg&h=f069d1c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1c74ed293e4a6f212892823cd71260032bb6fce","tid":1570462,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:48:35.000Z","msg":"其實唔止CWB<br />\n金鐘、中環、灣仔都有"},{"pid":"5e8ff30dad315d2af5140e0b524c005578f5a7ee","tid":1570462,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r